### Health check
GET https://chatgpt-team.pages.dev/v1/health

###

### Model listing
GET https://chatgpt-team.pages.dev/v1/models
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}

###

### Chat completions (non-stream)
POST https://chatgpt-team.pages.dev/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "Say hello" }],
  "stream": false
}

###

### Chat completion (streaming)
POST https://chatgpt-team.pages.dev/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "Stream me" }],
  "stream": true
}
